title: I Want to Help Enter Data W/ BGTX North Texas
description: Sign-up to show your interest in helping enter data with BGTX North Texas. Once you are signed up, we will reach out will information. Data entry can be done at any place and time, so we will work around your availability.

title: I Want to Help Deliver Forms W/ BGTX North Texas
description: Sign-up to show your interest in helping deliver forms with BGTX North Texas. Once you are signed up, we will reach out will information. Form delivery can be done M-F 8am-5pm, and we will work around your availability.

title: I Want BGTX North Texas to Deliver Voter Registration Forms
description: Sign-up to show your interest in having BGTX North Texas deliver your completed voter registration forms. Once you are signed up, we will reach out with more information. We can deliver forms in 15 North Texas counties, and will meet you to collect the forms and provide a receipt upon delivery to the election offices.

title: I Want to Lead a Voter Registration Event W/ BGTX North Texas
description: Sign-up to show your interest in leading a voter registration event with BGTX North Texas. Once you are signed up, we will reach out with more information. We can provide training and supplies to help make your event a success.

title: I want to register high school students to vote in Houston!
description:
Want to register Texas high school voters but don't know where to start? 
We've got your back!  

Sign up if you are: 
- Interested in having Student Voter Initiative (SVI) out to your high school.
- Excited to volunteer at events where you can register high school students. 
- Requesting SVI Organizers to register students at an upcoming event

Our team will contact you within 24 hours to walk you through the process.

title: I want to register college students to vote!
description:
Want to register Texas college students to vote but don't know where to start? 

We've got your back!  

Sign up if you are: 
- Interested in being a Battleground Texas Volunteer leader on your campus.
- Excited to volunteer at events where you can register students on college campuses.
- Requesting BGTX Organizers to register voters at an upcoming event.

Our team will contact you within 24 hours to walk you through the process.

title: I want to register voters at tax offices in Harris County!
description:
Want to meet people where they are and register them to vote? Tax offices are a great place to engage with the community. 

Our team will contact you within 24 hours to walk you through the process.

title: Register Voters @ Jazzy Sundays in the Park - The Suffers (Downtown Houston)
description:
This concert series aims to increase awareness of the city’s contributions to the Jazz art form and bring Houstonians together to enjoy its cultural heritage.

Join Battleground Texas as we enter the community and bring more people into the electoral process. We’ll meet new people and talk to them about the importance of voting, showing them how easy it is to register and make their voices heard.

Don’t forget to bring your volunteer deputy registrar certificate! RSVP below if you can make it.

title: Register Voters @ The Walk for Wellness (Spring Branch)
description:
Spring Branch Community Health Center created the Walk for Wellness as a way to engage and educate families in the community about the importance of healthy lifestyles and physical activity. The goal is to raise awareness and educate the community about chronic health issues.

Join Battleground Texas as we enter the community and bring more people into the electoral process. We’ll meet new people and talk to them about the importance of voting, showing them how easy it is to register and make their voices heard.

title: Battleground Texas: Statewide Information Session
description: Join us and discuss best practices for finding people who need to register to vote, convincing them to complete the voter registration form, making a plan to follow up with them to vote, staying compliant with the law, exercising all your rights as a Deputy Registrar, organizing voter registration drives, and much more! Whether you’re a newly minted Deputy Registrar or a seasoned veteran VDR, you’re sure to pick up a few new tricks at this training.
